      "title": "SSP Ruwan Gunasekera appointed Director of Police Legal Division",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Attorney-at-Law SSP Ruwan Gunasekera has been appointed as the Director of the Legal Division of Sri Lanka Police.",
        "The appointment was made by Inspector-General of Police (IG) C.D. Wickramaratne, the police media division said in a statement.",
        "The appointment is effective from August 22, subject to the approval of the Secretary of the Ministry of Public Security."
      ],
